name: Counts of isopods sampled at Gazi Bay (Kenya) between 18 and 25 October 1994
description: In October 1994, the hyperbenthos of Gazi Bay was sampled at 38 locations using a hyperbenthicsledge to studythe diversity of isopods. Sampling (day andnight) was conducted in as many differenthabitats as possible. The data were digitized by VLIZ fromtheoriginal report: De Bont, R. (1999). Diversiteit van de isopodenvan Gazi Bay (Kenia)= Diversity of the isopods of GaziBay, Kenya. Thesis. Universiteit Gent: Ghent. 28 pp.
